text: Alice Franco (born 10 February 1989) is an Italian female swimmer bronze medal at senior level at the 2011 World Aquatics Championships. She also was twice Europan champion, in 2011 and 2012. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female swimmers Category:Swimmers of Gruppo Sportivo Esercito Category:Italian female long- distance swimmers
